# UX Standards

- Shell navigation only via `AppNavigationDestinations` / `app_navigation.dart`
- Haptic + visual feedback on tab changes and primary actions
- Loading, error, and empty states must be intentional
- Touch targets ≥ 48dp; tooltips on icon-only controls
- Primary content fills space; thin chrome

Load `.cursor/skills/project/ux/SKILL.md` when designing or reviewing UI. Run the pre-ship checklist before finishing UI work.
